metadata.name: Lost In Thoughts
metadata.description:
Sometimes we end up getting lost in a web of our thoughts which our subconscious is webbing for days, months, or maybe years. All of these thoughts reflect our actions which ultimately define us. Having some notions about deep thoughts, it looks like it's been on a run constantly in our mind like a loop with layers of ideas and events. Getting lost in this layers of thoughts has its metaverse, that metavesrse is not on blockchain but its definitely on thought-chain. 
So, Where are you lost at ?

Sound track : Dreamer By Hazy - No Copyright Music
1200 X 1500 - 35:00 seconds loop
24 fps
